General.Name: Genesis Growth Tech Acquisition Corp Unit
General.Description: Genesis Growth Tech Acquisition Corp. does not have significant operations. It focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities. The company intends to focus its efforts on identifying technology companies operating primarily within the consumer internet industry in Europe, Israel, the United Arab Emirates, or the United States. Genesis Growth Tech Acquisition Corp. was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Hergiswil, Switzerland.
